data.description: Welcome to your dream home in the vibrant community of Asbel Estates, where modern luxury and convenience converge! This stunning, newer construction residence boasts 3 bedrooms, 2 1/2 bathrooms, and a spacious 2-car garage, providing the perfect blend of comfort and style. As you step inside, you'll be greeted by a thoughtfully designed floor plan that features living spaces on both the first and second floors. The main level offers a welcoming atmosphere with an open-concept layout, providing an ideal space for entertaining friends and family. The well-appointed kitchen is a chef's delight, featuring sleek countertops, contemporary appliances, and ample storage. Retreat to the second floor, where you'll find a tranquil haven in the form of three generously sized bedrooms. The master suite is a true sanctuary, complete with a private ensuite bathroom, offering a soothing escape after a long day. The additional bedrooms are versatile, making them perfect for a growing family, guests, or even a home office. Enjoy the Florida sunshine in the expansive backyard, surrounded by a large fenced-in area that ensures privacy and security. This outdoor space is perfect for hosting barbecues, playing with pets, or simply unwinding in your own oasis. Located in the desirable Asbel Estates community, you'll be just moments away from all that the Suncoast Parkway has to offer. Whether you're seeking outdoor adventures, shopping excursions, or dining experiences, this prime location provides easy access to a myriad of amenities. Don't miss the opportunity to make this house your home.
